{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286070/extras/promote_game.png?t=1737923179\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">About the Game</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Tale of REN is a Visual Novel that immerses players in the journey of Mizu Ren Nanami, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">a character sent to a distant world to gather the </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;Water of Heart&quot;\u2014a vital key to saving the world of Ren, which is on the brink of collapse. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Players will experience a complex and multi-layered story where choices impact the storyline, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">leading to various endings that can be selected as desired.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286070/extras/features.png?t=1737923179\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-Average playtime of 12-15 hours, depending on exploration and player decisions</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-Choice-based paths that influence the storyline and endings</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-Perfect for players who enjoy building relationships between characters</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-Engaging comic-style graphics</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-Hundreds of special illustrations and background scenes to create an immersive atmosphere</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-Unlockable gallery and music tracks</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-Journal system for taking personal notes throughout gameplay</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286070/extras/story.png?t=1737923179\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the land of Ren, every youth who reaches the age of 16 and passes a critical test must embark on a journey to fulfill a noble mission\u2014to seek the elusive Spirit Dew.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">I am Mizu Ren Nanami... As a native of Ren, my time has come to set forth on a journey to win the hearts of people in distant lands. My destination is the city of Rostania, and the young souls at the academy here are the ones with whom I must forge bonds to obtain the Spirit Dew.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Yet, as I undertake this mission, shadows of secrets from the past emerge, revealing truths I had never known...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286070/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737923179","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286070/page.bg.jpg?t=1737923179","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286070/5138837c97996768cfaf7182059e05fd38f60adb/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737923179","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286070/5138837c97996768cfaf7182059e05fd38f60adb/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737923179","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":2332830,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2286070/extras/promote_game.png?t=1737923179\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">About the Game</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Tale of REN is a Visual Novel that immerses players in the journey of Mizu Ren Nanami, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">a character sent to a distant world to gather the </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;Water of Heart&quot;\u2014a vital key to saving the world of Ren, which is on the brink of collapse. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Players will experience a complex and multi-layered story where choices impact the storyline, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">leading to various endings